---
title: Hearty Moroccan Chicken & Veggie Curry with Basmati Rice & Coriander
description: Enjoy the medley of fragrant flavours in this Moroccan-spiced curry with a gentle warming heat. Make it a low fuss meal that doesn't sacrifice on flavour with chermoula chicken adding to the creamy roast veggie curry sauce.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
